description: Empty & move in ready! This expansive condo features hardwood floors throughout and an open kitchen/living room perfect for entertaining. Key Features- Kitchen: Granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas range, and a cozy breakfast nook. Living Room: Spacious with abundant natural light, dental molding, and chair rails. Bedrooms: Two ample-sized bedrooms. Bathrooms: 1.5 baths, both with marble finishes; one includes a jacuzzi tub. Amenities: In-unit laundry, back deck, central A/C, deeded storage, and one off-street parking spot available for rent, walking distance to public transportation (bus & Red Line), and easy access to highways. This charming condo ideally located close to Southie’s best restaurants, shops, and newest developments making it a perfect spot for both relaxation and convenience. Whether you want to enjoy the cozy vibes as is or put in a little TLC to make it uniquely yours, this home is full of possibilities. 100% owner occupied! Motivated sellers!
